sources.title: Gamera tai uchu kaijû Bairasu (1968)
sources.description: As alien invaders plot to conquer the Earth, two Boy Scouts steal a mini-submarine and discover Gamera in their midst. Transported to the alien's spaceship, the Scouts are menaced by the evil inhabitants, including Viras, a squid-like monster that grows to colossal size to battle Gamera. Watch on RetroFlix:  https://retroflix.org/gamera-tai-uchu-kaiju-bairasu-1968/
